<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1396] Improve PhraseQuery.toString()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1396</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PhraseQuery.toString() is overly simplistic, in that it doesn&apos;t correctly show phrases with gaps or overlapping terms. This may be misleading when presenting phrase queries built using complex analyzers and filters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
